column7: Hello there! I am a chilled flavorful popsicle of the NFT (nifty) Joysicles. -A fun loving frozen flavor on a stick who loves long dips in the freezer followed by long hot summer days in the shade._new_line__new_line_Come Collect them all before they melt!
